| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7153 — Recovery Inhibition (shinyhunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5e046b76-2c40-5fbc-84a6-e41d15ccaa7b"
